title: Exploring China's Past (Art Ebook)
description:
Exploring China's Past: New Discoveries and Studies in Archaeology and Art
Saffron | 1999 | ISBN: 1872843255 | English | 292 pages | PDF | 41 MB

Presents up-to-date material on Chinese archaeology and art, written by a number of leading Chinese archaeologists. The chapters present new material and ideas on debate and practice, theoretical and methodological approaches, the origins of the Chinese civilization, ritual and sacrifice, social structures and belief systems. Includes a chapter on important discoveries between 1991 and 1995
